flowchart TB
    subgraph "Slack Vitess Architecture"
        A[Application] --> B[VTGate<br/>Query Router]
        B --> C1[Shard 1<br/>VTTablet]
        B --> C2[Shard 2<br/>VTTablet]
        B --> C3[Shard N<br/>VTTablet]

        D[VReplication] -.->|Migrate data| C1
        D -.->|Migrate data| C2
    end
